      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CLARICE (7) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including eight wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (30.13) when second at Cannington in a OPEN. Makes strong appeal on best. GEORDIE LAD (8) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by half a length at this track in a handy 27.66 beating Aston Bradley. Wide box to overcome but goes well over this trip. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Will go close again if runs up to latest. BILLY ME GOAT (1) was in hot form, winning four on end before colliding in the run last time and finishing fourth in a Grade 5 at this track (28.11). Has the ability and can atone with the right run. SUNSET LIGHTFOOT (2) in the money here last time and looks a top-three prospect again.",
